oGC73","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"recFPPmYLHmfePYj9","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"recjqxIrJX2UB8DdR","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"recZsS2Zu0zIDwqdv","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"reco82mzy0XTzaOgv","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"reczeMGDnN4eb0Y28","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"rec3YlUMCDBYgpxsL","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"recRjyN6AHqIvF4Ev","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMJ7MRpni7UXKmU","target":"recKRsEFLaEueJvei","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recTzgCJhgjyXyIXA","ref":"1Sam.19.1","text":"And Saul spake to Jonathan his son, and to all his servants, that they should kill David.","year":-1062},{"id":"reckoaOHJPpGpltZX","ref":"1Sam.19.2","text":"But Jonathan Saul’s son delighted much in David: and Jonathan told David, saying, Saul my father seeketh to kill thee: now therefore, I pray thee, take heed to thyself until the morning, and abide in a secret place, and hide thyself:","year":-1062},{"id":"recAcLQbgiI2JRGRY","ref":"1Sam.19.3","text":"And I will go out and stand beside my father in the field where thou art, and I will commune with my father of thee; and what I see, that I will tell thee.","year":-1062},{"id":"recdtzUDeNE6eMsVT","ref":"1Sam.19.4","text":"And Jonathan spake good of David unto Saul his father, and said unto him, Let not the king sin against his servant, against David; because he hath not sinned against thee, and because his works have been to thee-ward very good:","year":-1062},{"id":"rech3f1RDv6aEEalO","ref":"1Sam.19.5","text":"For he did put his life in his hand, and slew the Philistine, and the LORD wrought a great salvation for all Israel: thou sawest it, and didst rejoice: wherefore then wilt thou sin against innocent blood, to slay David without a cause?","year":-1062},{"id":"rec1JYjNo8qekTPLt","ref":"1Sam.19.6","text":"And Saul hearkened unto the voice of Jonathan: and Saul sware, As the LORD liveth, he shall not be slain.","year":-1062},{"id":"recFQTQ73yxf81Sm4","ref":"1Sam.19.7","text":"And Jonathan called David, and Jonathan shewed him all those things. And Jonathan brought David to Saul, and he was in his presence, as in times past.","year":-1062},{"id":"recWSCxlysTkl56Eo","ref":"1Sam.19.8","text":"And there was war again: and David went out, and fought with the Philistines, and slew them with a great slaughter; and they fled from him.","year":-1062}]}
